pt.up.fe.dceg.neptus.imc

Class IMCMessageType

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.up.fe.dceg.neptus.imc.IMCMessageType

  • public class IMCMessageType
extends java.lang.Object
    When parsing the messages definition file, an hashtable is filled with the supported message structures. This class holds information about a message like its size, name and fields.

    ZP
